{"id": "art-4851", "label": "Art. 4851", "title": "Art. 4851: Evaluarea performanţelor profesionale individuale ale funcţionarilor publici care ocupă funcţii publice prevăzute de art. 385 alin. (1) şi (2), pe bază de competenţe", "slug": "art-4851", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_700364478\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1196\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_700364478\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 485<sup>1</sup>:\nEvaluarea performan&#355;elor profesionale individuale ale func&#355;ionarilor\npublici care ocup&#259; func&#355;ii publice prev&#259;zute de art. 385 alin.\n(1) &#351;i (2), pe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1710051235\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1195\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1710051235\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Evaluarea performan&#355;elor profesionale individuale\nale func&#355;ionarilor publici care ocup&#259; func&#355;ii publice\nprev&#259;zute de art. 385 alin. (1) &#351;i (2), pe baz&#259; de\ncompeten&#355;e, se face anual.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_902506644\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1194\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_902506644\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Procesul de evaluare a performan&#355;elor profesionale\nindividuale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici de conducere &#351;i ale\nfunc&#355;ionarilor publici de execu&#355;ie prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1),\npe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e, reprezint&#259; aprecierea obiectiv&#259; a\nperforman&#355;elor profesionale individuale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici,\nprin verificarea modului de îndeplinire a obiectivelor individuale, utilizând\ncadrele de competen&#355;e generale &#351;i nivelurile de complexitate\naferente, precum &#351;i descriptorii &#351;i indicatorii comportamentali\naferen&#355;i competen&#355;elor generale stabilite pentru func&#355;iile\npublice prev&#259;zute la art. 390 &#351;i 392, conform art. 17 din anexa nr.\n8.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_950215259\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1193\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_950215259\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Stabilirea obiectivelor individuale trebuie s&#259;\naib&#259; în vedere corelarea cu atribu&#355;iile &#351;i obiectivele\ninstitu&#355;iei în care î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea\nfunc&#355;ionarul public.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1120563038\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1192\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1120563038\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Evaluarea performan&#355;elor profesionale individuale\npe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e se realizeaz&#259; pentru to&#355;i\nfunc&#355;ionarii publici prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1) care au\ndesf&#259;&#351;urat efectiv activitate, minimum 6 luni, în anul calendaristic\npentru care se realizeaz&#259; evaluarea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_239560759\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1191\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_239560759\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Calificativele\nob&#355;inute în procesul de evaluare a performan&#355;elor profesionale\nindividuale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1),\npe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e, sunt avute în vedere la:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_296102629\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1190\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_296102629\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)promovarea într-o func&#355;ie public&#259;\nsuperioar&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2011044465\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1189\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2011044465\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)acordarea de prime, în condi&#355;iile legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1211030434\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1188\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1211030434\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)diminuarea drepturilor salariale cu 10% pân&#259; la\nurm&#259;toarea evaluare anual&#259; a performan&#355;elor profesionale\nindividuale pe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e, pentru func&#355;ionarii publici\ncare au ob&#355;inut calificativul «satisf&#259;c&#259;tor»;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1613568297\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1187\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1613568297\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)eliberarea din func&#355;ia public&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_584401599\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1186\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_584401599\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Evaluarea performan&#355;elor profesionale individuale\nale func&#355;ionarilor publici prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1), pe baz&#259;\nde competen&#355;e, se realizeaz&#259; în mod obligatoriu la modificarea,\nsuspendarea &#351;i încetarea raporturilor de serviciu ale func&#355;ionarilor\npublici.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1669471775\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1185\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1669471775\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)În cadrul procesului de evaluare a performan&#355;elor\nprofesionale individuale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici prev&#259;zu&#355;i la\nalin. (1), pe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e, se stabilesc cerin&#355;ele de\nformare profesional&#259; a func&#355;ionarilor publici.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1073552242\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1184\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1073552242\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Procesul de evaluare a performan&#355;elor profesionale\nindividuale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1),\npe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e, se desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; cu respectarea\nmetodologiei de evaluare a performan&#355;elor profesionale individuale ale\nfunc&#355;ionarilor publici pe baz&#259; de competen&#355;e, care se\naprob&#259; prin lege.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) prevederile art. 398<sup>1</sup>\n&#351;i 485<sup>1</sup> se aplic&#259; începând cu data de 1 ianuarie 2025\npentru func&#355;ionarii publici care ocup&#259; func&#355;ii publice\nprev&#259;zute la art. 385 alin. (1) &#351;i (2).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}